name: Experiment Or Die #106
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. The 11th letter in The Cool Alphabet, H is for Heisenberg. If you immediately don't know who Heisenberg is then you are missing out on one of the greatest series of raw entertainment in existence. Breaking Bad broke every mold for a series and forever set the tone for edgy, controversial and dramatic television. Heisenberg started out as the every man that we can all relate to in a desperate situation and ended as a ruthless kingpin molded from necessity, ambition and greed. We all have the best intentions but often where we end up is nowhere near where we were headed. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
